<br>
But I always had as many pets as I could get.<br>
<br>
I prefered Air up to level 29, then went with fire up to level 49. (Having a Cleric in the group helps make that the best decision.)<br>
<br>
At level 49 I got all my pets researched and I'm still very happy I have them. The Air pet is great in places like Hate (Where rooting mobs is BAD and Fire pets die in seconds.) The 49 Fire pet is STILL the pet of choice against Rak Ashir in City of Mist. 49 Earth was the dungeon tank of choice though to stop runners and tank adds without any trouble. (Even in Chardok he's a champ.)<br>
